data.description: Welcome home to this lovely 4 bedroom, 3 bath home located in the Olde Mill Subdivision. Upon entering you are welcomed into a large den with fireplace and  separate formal dining room. The spacious kitchen with island boasts a plethora of cabinet and counter space. This home has a downstairs master suite showcasing a large closet. Throughout the home flows beautiful hardwood and plush carpeting. The fenced in backyard makes the outside deck a perfect place to find your oasis or entertain guests as it over looks the plush lawn.  This home is conveniently located minutes away from MUSC, restaurants, schools and shopping.
